---
title: Sichuan Glazed Pork & Sesame Kumara Fries with Pear Salad & Mayo
description: A hot contender for 'best new accompaniment', the punchy Sichuan garlic paste in this dish really takes it to the next level. We're serving it with mouth-watering garlic pork steaks, golden sesame-flecked kumara wedges and a fresh pear salad.

*Unfortunately, this week's tomato was in short supply, so we've replaced it with green pear. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
